# Xterm Background Mode

## Chạy với font + auto-close

```bash
xterm -fa 'Ubuntu Sans Mono' -fs 13 -title "Claude" -e "./script.sh" &
```

## Flags

| Flag | Mô tả |
|------|-------|
| `-fa 'Ubuntu Sans Mono'` | Font family |
| `-fs 13` | Font size |
| `-title "X"` | Tiêu đề |
| `-e "cmd"` | Chạy command |
| `&` | Background |

## Auto-close

Script tự close sau 30s (trong `autoclaude-loop.sh`):
```bash
echo ">>> Closing in 30s..."
sleep 30
```

## Verified

✅ 2025-12-03 - Font size 14, auto-close 30s
